Underlying Business Problems: - Sending all users emails without considering activeness - Replacing emails with chatbots - Using emails to get input from users rather

1. Limiting Users:
   - Limiting users who receive the daily remainder
   - This can be possible by using last vote by the user
   - If the user didn't vote for past few weeks, suspend sending daily emails
2. Chatbots:
   - Email Delivery Services are resource consuming
   - Chatbots are lite and can make the chats more interactive
